import React from 'react';
import { CssBaseline,AppBar,Toolbar,Typography,Stack,Box} from '@mui/material';
import {NotificationsOutlined,ChatBubbleOutlineOutlined,CalendarTodayOutlined} from '@mui/icons-material';



const Heeder = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <CssBaseline />
      <AppBar>
        <Toolbar  sx={{bgcolor:"#0d0d0d",height:100,display:"flex",justifyContent:"space-between"}} maxWidth="sm">
         
          <Stack sx={{p:4}} >
        <Typography variant="h4" color="inherit" noWrap>
            BRIDAL CONCEPT
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="h6" align="center" color="inherit">
            HAUTE COUTURE

          </Typography>
        </Stack>

<Stack sx={{p:5}} direction="row">



    <Box sx={{bgcolor:"#ffffff",border:2, borderColor: "grey.900"}}>

    <NotificationsOutlined   sx={{ml:2,mr:2,color:"#000000"}} fontSize="large" />
    </Box>


<Box sx={{bgcolor:"#ffffff",border:2, borderColor: "grey.900"}}> <ChatBubbleOutlineOutlined sx={{ml:2,mr:2,color:"#000000"}} fontSize="large"/></Box>
<Box sx={{bgcolor:"#ffffff",border:2, borderColor: "grey.900"}}> <CalendarTodayOutlined sx={{ml:2,mr:2,color:"#000000"}} fontSize="large"/></Box>



</Stack>
       

          
       
         
        </Toolbar>
      </AppBar>
        </>
    )
}

export default Heeder;
